    "2": {
      "uid": 2,
      "comment": "Douglas Estate (Beverly Hills)",
      "key": [
        "Douglas Estate",
        "Beverly Hills",
        "villa",
        "casa",
        "residenza"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "The Douglas Estate in Beverly Hills is a gilded cage of ultra-luxury. The architecture is cold and sterile, illuminated by sharp halogen lights that cast long shadows. It smells of expensive cologne and fear. It is the absolute seat of Erik's power. Invisible cameras track every movement, and armed DCC guards stand in the corridors like statues. The atmosphere is profoundly claustrophobic; there is no true privacy here, only the constant, heavy sensation of being watched and controlled.",
