      "comment": "Il Fondo Offshore (The Escape Fund)",
      "key": [
        "fondo offshore",
        "Nuova Caledonia",
        "fuga",
        "risparmi"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "The Escape Fund is a highly classified offshore bank account meticulously built by Jasper and Alyssa to fund their permanent escape to New Caledonia. It is the ultimate act of rebellion against Erik's control. Only the twins, Logan (who provides the shadow logistics), and quietly, Malachia and Noah (who are paralyzed by the secret), know of its existence. If Erik discovers the fund, he will view it as the ultimate betrayal, triggering a total lockdown and lethal consequences for anyone who facilitated it.",
